channel.title: ►CaliberScape V2 is up for download! Come give it a look.◄
channel.description:
[IMG]http://i94.photobucket.com/albums/l82/lilgenius095/Calibersig.png[/img]
Welcome to my topic. In this topic you will find the newly released server source that is known as CaliberScape. This is the second version. You can still download V1 if you like. I think this source should be pretty stable after some coding. I hope you enjoy it. [hr]
Please keep this topic alive and make a positive or negative post.
/*/Commands/*/ [code] IPban xteletomeisland (made for a friend) Ele Eleoff Joinclan Clan Jump Jump off Chicken Chicken Off Swim Climb Climb Off Matrix Matrix Off Car Car off Magiccarpet Magiccarpetoff Chill *Famous/Classic* Dropparty (Admin+) Obj (::obj [Item code] ... This is in your server file. Autoobject.txt) PK Gay [Playername] Ground Fall DBmini Pickup (You know how to use this) Dtmini Office Jail [PLAYERNAME] Unjail [PLAYERNAME] Alltome (Xteleall) Eat Rep [Playername] Pure Noted Barrows Alert [Message] Lupdate [Message] Pnpc [NPC ID] Makeadmin [Playername] Demote [PLAYERNAME] Makemod [Name] Cwars M (Money) Starter Xteletome Xteleto God Money Sweet Jad WC Kqueen Cather 3rdage Edge PKBox Zammy Slayer Smith Guilds Shops TeamPK Train Skill Barrows Mining Makemem [PLAYERNAME] Bandos Suggest ImasterI Owner Food[/code]
The first one here is the Bandos Minigame. If you can tackle all four waves, you get full Bandos.
[IMG]http://i94.photobucket.com/albums/l82/lilgenius095/Bmini-1.png[/img]
Working Crackers. To get one, click the chest and you will get a cracker. To remove the chest, it should be the last code added.
[IMG]http://i94.photobucket.com/albums/l82/lilgenius095/Cracker-1.png[/img]
Crackers working. I'm using one here...
[IMG]http://i94.photobucket.com/albums/l82/lilgenius095/Home-4.png[/img]
This is the new PKBox. Thanks to my little brother for the cool location. There is a safe zone in both sides. Download and check it out.
[IMG]http://i94.photobucket.com/albums/l82/lilgenius095/Pkbox-1.png[/img]
This is the skill area. Thanks to the nubcake who made it on the Silabsoft forums. :P
[IMG]http://i94.photobucket.com/albums/l82/lilgenius095/Skillingarea-1.png[/img]
And this is how it looks when you use a cracker on someone.
[IMG]http://i94.photobucket.com/albums/l82/lilgenius095/Crackers.png[/img]
Thank you for viewing my server download. I hope to see someone hosting it in the future.
